abstract: Athletic Bilbao beats Barcelona, 4-0, in first leg of Spanish Super Cup; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Athletic Bilbao roared to a stunning 4-0 victory over visiting Barcelona in the first leg of the Spanish Super Cup.
